<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Klack und <expan>l<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, von des knechts und der frawen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die bey ewch in fenknuss
                                <expan>lige<ex>n</ex></expan>, schiken wir
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu ewch <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Yachstorff<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden, und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch mit fleiss, was
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gelawben und ewch darinn so
                                <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, als etc. Das wellen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>corp<ex>or</ex>is</expan> Christi.</ab>
